[assistant] - Replaced the `NativeLibrary.getInstance("c").getFile()` approach with a safer helper that locates an existing loadable native library from:
[assistant]   - `${java.home}/lib/libjava.so`
[assistant]   - `${java.home}/lib/server/libjvm.so`
[assistant]   - common Linux `libc.so.6` locations
